<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ZORA</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.jpg">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/styles.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        .split-hero {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            min-height: 100vh;
            border-top: var(--border-thick);
        }

        .hero-title-big {
            font-family: var(--font-heading);
            font-size: 15rem;
            line-height: 0.75;
            letter-spacing: -0.05em;
            color: var(--accent-orange);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .hero-magazine-box {
            padding: 8rem 10%;
            background: white;
            border-right: var(--border-thin);
        }

        .hero-magazine-image {
            background: url('/images/two.png') center/cover no-repeat;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero-magazine-image::after {
            content: 'MAGAZINE';
            position: absolute;
            top: 4rem;
            right: -2rem;
            font-family: var(--font-heading);
            font-size: 8rem;
            color: white;
            transform: rotate(90deg);
            transform-origin: top right;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <div class="middle-nav">
            <div style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; width: 100px;">EST.
                2026<br>EDITION 01</div>
            <div class="brand-main">ZORA</div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
                <% if (typeof currentUser !=='undefined' && currentUser) { %>
                    <a href="/home" class="btn-orange" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;">HOME</a>
                    <a href="/home/create" class="btn-orange"
                        style="padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px;">PUBLISH</a>
                    <a href="/logout" style="color: black; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-left: 1rem;"><i
                            class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i></a>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <a href="/login" class="btn-orange">LOGIN</a>
                        <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="split-hero">
            <div class="hero-magazine-box">
                <div
                    style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    ISSUE 01 &bull; SPECIAL EDITION</div>
                <h1 class="hero-title-big">ZO<br>RA</h1>
                <p
                    style="font-size: 1.5rem; border-top: var(--border-thick); padding-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;">
                    A curated collection of digital stories, research, and designer perspectives from across the globe.
                </p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 2rem;">
                    <a href="/login" class="btn-orange" style="font-size: 1.25rem; padding: 1rem 3rem;">Enter Zora</a>
                    <a href="/signup"
                        style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.25rem; padding: 1rem; border: var(--border-thick); display: flex; align-items: center; text-decoration: none; color: black; font-weight: 700;">JOIN
                        US</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-magazine-image"></div>
        </div>

        <section
            style="padding: 10rem 4%; background: var(--text-black); color: white; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8rem;">
            <div>
                <h2
                    style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 6rem; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 0.9;">
                    The Art of Content.</h2>
            </div>
            <div
                style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; border-left: 1px solid #333; padding-left: 4rem;">
                <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Zora is an elite editorial ecosystem. A global
                    definitive for high-fashion narratives, architectural research, and the evolution of the modern
                    silhouette.</p>
                <p style="color: #888;">Bridge the gap between fast-paced digital media and the timeless, intentional
                    quality of high-end curation.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section style="padding: 10rem 4%; background: white; border-top: var(--border-thick);">
            <h2
                style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 8rem; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 0.8; margin-bottom: 6rem; letter-spacing: -4px;">
                THE<br>MANIFESTO</h2>
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 4rem;">
                <div style="border-top: 2px solid black; padding-top: 2rem;">
                    <h3
                        style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-orange);">
                        01 / CURATION</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #666;">We believe in the power of the filtered
                        lens. In an age of digital noise, Zora serves as a steady hand, selecting only the narratives
                        that possess genuine architectural and cultural weight.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="border-top: 2px solid black; padding-top: 2rem;">
                    <h3
                        style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-orange);">
                        02 / STRUCTURE</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #666;">Our design philosophy is rooted in the
                        intersection of movement and logic. Every story we publish is analyzed for its structural
                        integrity and its contribution to the modern silhouette.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="border-top: 2px solid black; padding-top: 2rem;">
                    <h3
                        style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-orange);">
                        03 / PRESERVATION</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #666;">Digital doesn't have to mean temporary.
                        We treat every digital artifact with the same reverence as a physical archive, ensuring that
                        high-fashion history is preserved for future generations.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer style="padding: 8rem 4%; text-align: center; border-top: var(--border-thick);">
        <div class="brand-main" style="font-size: 20rem; opacity: 0.05;">ZORA</div>
        <p style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 2rem; margin-top: -5rem;">GET INSPIRED TODAY.</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>